reviews.content:
if you can put up with the length, this film has it all;
action, mystery, thrills, surprises, intelligence, a love story, a reunion, a heartless corporate overlord.  existential debate and nihilistic vs, religious overtones. 
The cast in this movie owned their roles conveying the gravity of duty and gritty  self sacrifice. The cinematography, lighting, sets  and sounds are all surreal in ways that echo the familiar. Bravo!
